import React from 'react'
import { TextField, Button, Box } from '@mui/material'


export default function Login() {
    return (
        <Box sx={{
            '& .MuiTextField-root:': {
                m: 1,
                width: '90%'
            }
        }}>
            <form noValidate autoComplete='off'>
                <TextField
                    label="Email"
                    name="email"
                    variant="outlined" />
                <TextField
                    label="Name"
                    name="name"
                    variant="outlined" />
                <Button
                    type="submit"
                    variant="contained"
                    size="large">Start</Button>
            </form>
        </Box>
    )
}
